antes → poca evidencia para TVC","guid":"P65c4DL2QJK3rY2EI0DY6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"109","text":"VITT (Trombocitopenia\\NTrombotica Inducida por Vacuna)","guid":"jtSudGW5R_aGcYZOLdprDg","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Fisiopatologia DIFERENTE → similar a HIT","guid":"HaLm-D1KQHWPzdnB_vXXfA","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"NO usar heparina → contraindicada","guid":"e4QRp-QvS8eLmaY-QjyFJg","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"Anticoagulantes no heparinicos (argatroban, fondaparinux)","guid":"ID-JlxEpRkeJnP50Dk8Ngw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"151","text":"Inmunoglobulina IV","guid":"eERJzUrETpuXjHWX0bu60g","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"151","text":"Corticoides","guid":"Bl8ZgAWkT32MMzQVJhHG6Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"0","text":"Pronostico","guid":"XwhUxOwARrCgXBM-nnsNGg","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"GENERAL →\\Nbueno en mayoria","guid":"dVwHvw6QQ0uE15jrsyB_kw","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Mortalidad aguda: 2-4% (global)","guid":"ZiudGxsbQKCeQ9cFkBxezw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"Outcome favorable (mRS 0-2): 80-85%","guid":"Z-VCEwohRZaFJ0MUssZ-VA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"Recurrencia TVC: 2-4% a 2 anos","guid":"8RxIVtfVTNGxjLSJ0P6P3w","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"Recurrencia cualquier TEV: 4-7% a 2 anos","guid":"kMNtTkbPQqOGQcq-pJz--g","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"157","text":"FACTORES DE\\NMAL PRONOSTICO","guid":"ckEJsH41R1mZzhRO5Siwyw","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Coma al ingreso (GCS <9)","guid":"wHekCf1rQmCndg3ybFbWww","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Trombosis sistema venoso profundo","guid":"CMlwWXniTGusrgDgj8B7Vg","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"Hemorragia intracraneal al diagnostico","guid":"up-qhzXzSU6Dt_7h8u47WA","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"Cancer subyacente","guid":"2JcDGjKNRzKuk93VLBYMEA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"163","text":"Infeccion SNC","guid":"RxP12D4KTQebVpUxj3QgFQ","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"163","text":"Edad avanzada","guid":"j_5sYFbbROuYqoHQlns6Gg","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"163","text":"Sexo masculino","guid":"v-5uPx2vT3Kr2rLLT5HWEQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"157","text":"EN ADULTOS\\NMAYORES","guid":"D-ketDB0QYe27Eg4F7j_0w","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"Mortalidad fase aguda 8% (vs 1.7%)","guid":"5dcjfqGxTOCVLznz29wPqw","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"Outcome favorable 1 ano 73% (vs 87%)","guid":"63roMSp8S0a0mSKQPnLFfw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"Cancer como factor etiologico → peor pronostico","guid":"LOStBEpkRRKKGeHTITkoDw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriatricas","guid":"V7tbjH3eQJSEOa-BjSC7RQ","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Presentacion ATIPICA →\\Nalto indice de sospecha","guid":"rDEBhSt8TYGApGrGR1ILXg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Confusion/delirium como forma de presentacion","guid":"bRqpNKFAQ06l_lABvHwhVw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Menos cefalea clasica → no descartar por ausencia","guid":"D_S7b5YyS7KV3o6xTxKI9w","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"Convulsiones de novo en AM → buscar TVC","guid":"j2ReNxUIR-2n4Ye9RZWSiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"Diagnostico diferencial\\Namplio en AM","guid":"y5oRrYQyRHSiGFjk_KPXQg","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Delirium por otras causas","guid":"SgC2B2J3QMejIGJLQDJr9A","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"ACV arterial","guid":"vHsxIpjFQOCOZ5mWk2oyxA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"Meningitis/encefalitis","guid":"YCJVSZT2To6M3VTgaQ2MLg","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"Tumor con efecto de masa","guid":"X0SGVMkeTYutrPCZwc59BQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"175","text":"Etiologia → buscar NEOPLASIA y HEMOPATIA activamente","guid":"LBUzGC04RzyKE3zl3vYdEQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"175","text":"Anticoagulacion\\N→ considerar","guid":"9HjwAV0pQl-cixBtLlHxhQ","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"Riesgo hemorragico (HAS-BLED)","guid":"Ert3uuAYTIawbJ8EEZDSaQ","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"Funcion renal → ajustar HBPM si ClCr <30","guid":"vMEReobTSkey0ZecjxBvtQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"Interacciones farmacologicas (polifarmacia)","guid":"mefEAMDBQECSBjsxXHnt_Q","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"Riesgo de caidas → no contraindica per se","guid":"--zMp9XZSe2RowsKTk4YiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"175","text":"DOACs en AM → estudio\\NDOAC-CVT incluyo mediana 41a","guid":"MRTiAS8RSmW2Y_PISxFUKg","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"Datos limitados en >=65a","guid":"ptAS4Cp4S0y9_3gMMYMTgA","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"Mismas precauciones que en FA (funcion renal, peso)","guid":"r7snnG0kSSiC1TUcgw13yA","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"175","text":"Rehabilitacion precoz","guid":"RKG_m4gdQ5yCY0R7p_weZw","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"175","text":"Pronostico funcional → considerar CFS basal","guid":"DHVAR3IxR3CQYhPzejMquA","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClinicas","guid":"GM2y7pqMSACBJm9Ya7qtWQ","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"Cefalea progresiva + deficit focal + convulsiones = pensar TVC","guid":"CoyrulcnRMuqQmi3zstfhg","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"TC normal NO descarta TVC → pedir Angio-TC o RM venosa","guid":"lg8intyuRiylh4bNjdRjag","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"Anticoagulacion es SEGURA incluso con infarto hemorragico","guid":"EqbDKG90S-agi5hew6OVSw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"En AM: confusion de novo + convulsiones = buscar TVC","guid":"OempLAoaS1S1JJ4P9ncnSw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"196","tex